(42, 1, '2015-07-22 12:50:37', '2015-07-22 12:50:37', '<p>One Tower Bridge is situated on one of the last great riverside sites in London. Just moments from the City it offers the ultimate in 5-star luxury living experiences in the most exciting city in the world.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n• 24 hour Harrods concierge<br />\r\n• Iconic riverside location<br />\r\n• River view apartments with balconies or terraces, some with river views<br />\r\n• Luxury spa and gym facilities.</p>\r\n  \r\n<p>One Tower Bridge can boast some of the finest historical views and cultural landmarks in London including Tower Bridge, City Hall,  the Tower of London, the Gerkin together with the Shard being only a few moments away.  Along the river, both the London Eye and the Houses of Parliament stand out as striking features that are prominent of the London landscape.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>The area also offers opportunity to explore a wide variety of artistic tastes. With Shakespeare\'s Globe, Royal Festival Hall and the Old Vic within walking distance a play or performance is always an option or a visit to a gallery or a museum is never far away, being based in the heart of London\'s rich culture.</p>', 'One Tower Bridge', 'Tower Bridge SE1 2AA', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'one-tower-bridge', '', '', '2016-08-05 13:07:37', '2016-08-05 13:07:37', '', 0, 'http://inspirythemesdemo.com/realplaces/?post_type=property&#038;p=42', 0, 'property', '', 0),
(45, 1, '2015-07-22 13:25:03', '2015-07-22 13:25:03', '<p>190 Strand is a flagship development by St Edward, offering a range of bespoke apartments, townhouses and penthouses. Located on the world famous Strand, this new iconic landmark will be closely linked to the richest aspects of London living.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n•     24 hour concierge<br />\r\n•     World famous location<br />\r\n•     Stylish business suite<br />\r\n•     Luxurious swimming pool &amp; spa</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Located on the world famous Strand, 190 Strand is a new iconic landmark at the historical crossroads of a great city.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>190 Strand will be a luxurious new development of bespoke suites, apartments and penthouses in an area of central London internationally acknowledged as the Capital\'s theatre, shopping and cultural heartland with international embassies, law courts and the River Thames close by.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>190 Strand will offer a world class address, closely linked to the richest aspects of London living.</strong></p>\r\n', '190 Strand', 'Westminster WC2R 1DT', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '190-strand', '', '', '2016-08-16 06:18:41', '2016-08-16 06:18:41', '', 0, 'http://inspirythemesdemo.com/realplaces/?post_type=property&#038;p=45', 0, 'property', '', 0),
(91, 1, '2015-07-23 10:17:15', '2015-07-23 10:17:15', '<p>Royal Arsenal Riverside is one of South East London\'s most exciting riverside addresses, occupying a prime location along the River Thames with a forthcoming on-site Crossrail Station and buzzing retail hub.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     On-site Thames Clipper service <br />\r\n•     Close proximity to London City Airport<br />\r\n•     Fantastic range of on-site amenities<br />\r\n•     Over 1km of river walk<br />\r\n•     Forthcoming luxury spa and gym<br />\r\n•     300m away from National Rail and DLR stations\r\n</p>', 'Royal Arsenal Riverside', 'Woolwich SE18 6FR', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'royal-arsenal-riverside', '', '', '2016-08-04 18:00:36', '2016-08-04 18:00:36', '', 0, 'http://inspirythemesdemo.com/realplaces/?post_type=property&#038;p=91', 0, 'property', '', 0),
(94, 1, '2015-07-23 10:43:21', '2015-07-23 10:43:21', '<p>Set within the Borough of Richmond upon Thames, Brewery Wharf is a new development of 82 luxury apartments and 28 gated houses, 2 restaurants, public piazza and a cultural venue. Best known for world famous Twickenham Stadium, this area is much sought after due to its excellent schools, beautiful riverside walks, historical landmarks, museums and green open spaces.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     Close to Kingston &amp; Richmond<br />\r\n•     Excellent school catchment area<br />\r\n•     0.5 miles to the River Thames<br />\r\n•     Opposite Twickenham Train Station\r\n</p>\r\n \r\n<p>The regeneration of the former Royal Mail Sorting Office in Twickenham will produce a vibrant community with 110 residential homes, community building and public piazza.  But this is not the only thing that is planned for Twickenham.  It is part of a wider regeneration plan which will see millions of pounds ploughed into the area over the next 14 years.  Environmental improvements are being undertaken all over the borough as well as plans having been approved for the regeneration of Twickenham Station, bringing about improvement to make the station fit for the 21st century</p>', 'Brewery Wharf', 'Twickenham TW1 1AA', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'brewery-wharf', '', '', '2016-08-05 13:23:30', '2016-08-05 13:23:30', '', 0, 'http://inspirythemesdemo.com/realplaces/?post_type=property&#038;p=94', 0, 'property', '', 0),
(98, 1, '2015-07-23 11:42:53', '2015-07-23 11:42:53', '<p>Kidbrooke Village is located in one of London\'s most popular locations, the Royal Borough of Greenwich and comprises of four distinct neighbourhoods, integrated seamlessly into one community. These include: Meridian Gate, Blackheath Quarter, Kidbrooke Village Centre and City Point.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     Only 15 minutes to London Bridge<br />\r\n•     Highly desired SE3 postcode<br />\r\n•     Award winning development<br />\r\n•     136 acres of open space<br />\r\n </p>\r\n<p>A range of exclusive residents\' only facilities including Gymnasium, Business Centre, Swimming Pool and 24hr Concierge.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Kidbrooke Village is one of Berkeley\'s biggest regeneration projects to date, costing an estimated £1 billion, making it one of the largest residential developments in London. It consists of four distinct yet integrated neighbourhoods: City Point, Blackheath Quarter, Kidbrooke Village Centre and Meridian Gate, which between them will offer an outstanding choice of contemporary new homes and apartments to suit every type of buyer.</p>', 'Kidbrooke Village', 'Greenwich SE3 9FD', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kidbrooke-village', '', '', '2016-08-05 13:22:11', '2016-08-05 13:22:11', '', 0, 'http://inspirythemesdemo.com/realplaces/?post_type=property&#038;p=98', 0, 'property', '', 0),
(101, 1, '2015-07-23 11:49:44', '2015-07-23 11:49:44', '<p>One Blackfriars is set to be a beacon of architectural brilliance.  Rising 50 storeys and designed by award winning Simpson Haugh &amp; Partners Architects, it will add a shimmering new dimension to London\'s skyline.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     50 storey - 170m Tower <br />\r\n•     Stunning views of London<br />\r\n•     Moments from the River Thames<br />\r\n•     Luxury residents facilities<br />\r\n </p>\r\n<p>Designed by internationally renowned interior designers Tara Bernerd and Partners, the collections are named after leading British artists:  Thomas Gainsborough, the 18th century portrait and landscape painter; JMW Turner, revered for his Romantic and Impressionist landscapes and the 20th century Modernist sculptor Barbara Hepworth, to celebrate the cultural heritage of the South Bank.   The collections offer a range of apartments with a choice of two design schemes.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Maintaining the comfort of the residents at One Blackfriars is essential.  A wide range of facilities are conveniently on offer within the development, making it the perfect place for enjoyment and relaxation.  Facilities include a thermal spa with swimming pool, steam room, sauna and snow cabin, a fitness suite, private screening room, wine cellar and a stunning Executive Lounge on Level 32 where a private dining area can be pre booked.</p>', 'One Blackfriars', 'London SE1 9UF', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'one-blackfriars', '', '', '2016-08-05 13:16:53', '2016-08-05 13:16:53', '', 0, 'http://inspirythemesdemo.com/realplaces/?post_type=property&#038;p=101', 0, 'property', '', 0),
