(570, 1, '2016-08-03 12:08:55', '2016-08-03 12:08:55', '<p>London Dock by St George, situated just moments from Tower Bridge, the Tower of London, St Katharine Docks and the City. This exciting new destination in the heart of London, a thriving new cultural quarter, featuring a magnificent choreographed central water feature and the finest selection of high quality new homes.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     Discover 7.5 acres of new public space<br />\r\n•     Indulge in hotel-style residents facilities<br />\r\n•     Move in from Q3 2016<br />\r\n•     Explore new places to eat, drink and enjoy\r\n</p>\r\n<p>London Dock is the perfect place to unwind over lunch or dinner in the vibrant surroundings of Gauging Square, a stunning new space with spectacular interactive water features and a thriving mix of shops, bars and restaurants.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a number of London underground and Docklands Light Railway stations within walking distance, London Dock offers quick and easy access to London&#39;s main financial centres of the City and Canary Wharf, as well as the exciting cultural and creative neighborhoods of Shoreditch, Whitechapel and Bermondsey.</p>\r\n', 'London Deck', 'Dock St, London E1', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '569-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-03 12:08:55', '2016-08-03 12:08:55', '', 569, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/2016/08/03/569-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(403, 1, '2016-08-02 08:33:18', '2016-08-02 08:33:18', 'We are an award winning and very unique concept inspired by street food - Burgers + Kebabs and have elevated it to a modern day experience. Using the freshest of ingredients, custom meat blends, and unique flavors we pride ourselves on sourcing the highest quality products and carefully crafting each plate for an unforgettable experience.', 'Kidbrooke Village', 'Greenwich SE3 9FD', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '98-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-08-02 08:33:18', '2016-08-02 08:33:18', '', 98, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/2016/08/02/98-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(404, 1, '2016-08-02 08:34:24', '2016-08-02 08:34:24', '<p>Kidbrooke Village is located in one of London\'s most popular locations, the Royal Borough of Greenwich and comprises of four distinct neighbourhoods, integrated seamlessly into one community. These include: Meridian Gate, Blackheath Quarter, Kidbrooke Village Centre and City Point.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     Only 15 minutes to London Bridge<br />\r\n•     Highly desired SE3 postcode<br />\r\n•     Award winning development<br />\r\n•     136 acres of open space<br />\r\n </p>\r\n<p>A range of exclusive residents\' only facilities including Gymnasium, Business Centre, Swimming Pool and 24hr Concierge.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Kidbrooke Village is one of Berkeley\'s biggest regeneration projects to date, costing an estimated £1 billion, making it one of the largest residential developments in London. It consists of four distinct yet integrated neighbourhoods: City Point, Blackheath Quarter, Kidbrooke Village Centre and Meridian Gate, which between them will offer an outstanding choice of contemporary new homes and apartments to suit every type of buyer.</p>', 'Kidbrooke Village', 'Greenwich SE3 9FD', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '98-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-02 08:34:24', '2016-08-02 08:34:24', '', 98, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/2016/08/02/98-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
