(517, 1, '2016-08-03 09:22:49', '2016-08-03 09:22:49', '<p>Established as an exclusive waterside community, Battersea Reach has more to offer than just its fine living spaces. Residents can enjoy convenient living in enviable surroundings with picturesque grounds.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     Award winning gardens<br />\r\n•     Riverside walkways<br />\r\n•     Superb array of amenities<br />\r\n•     Excellent transport links\r\n</p>\r\n<p>With an array of amenities at Battersea Reach across the river allows you to enjoy the cafés, bars and shops in the King\'s Road, Knightsbridge and Kensington. Surrounded by green areas, Battersea benefits from a choice of Parks and commons such as Wimbledon Common and Hurlingham Park. Culture is easily accessible from Battersea Reach, capturing the City\'s West end for musicals, shows at the Royal Albert Hall, art and history in the galleries and museums.</p>', 'Battersea Reach', 'Wandsworth SW18 1TX', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'battersea-reach', '', '', '2016-08-03 09:29:15', '2016-08-03 09:29:15', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=517', 0, 'property', '', 0),
