(543, 1, '2016-08-03 10:17:44', '2016-08-03 10:17:44', '<p>Riverlight is an exciting new residential development, directly on the riverfront in the heart of the new Nine Elms on the South Bank district, London\'s largest and most exciting regeneration area.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     Prime riverfront location <br />\r\n•     Rogers StirkHarbour + Partners<br />\r\n•     Exclusive residents\' clubhouse<br />\r\n•     Heart of regeneration area\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Riverlight is a family of six pavilions, rising in height, all with a North-South orientation. Its thoughtful design is based on its riverside location and an emphasis on natural light. Each building features prow-like ends, floor to ceiling glazing and inverted balconies which aim to let in daylight and maximise views of both the river and the surrounding city, resulting in a design which is both practically and aesthetically sophisticated.</p>\r\n', 'Riverlight', 'Vauxhall SW8 5BP', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'riverlight', '', '', '2016-08-05 13:13:00', '2016-08-05 13:13:00', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=543', 0, 'property', '', 0),
