(558, 1, '2016-08-03 11:27:40', '2016-08-03 11:27:40', '<p>Woodberry Down is a new luxury development in North London, located on the banks of the New River and West and East Reservoirs overlooking more than 42 acres of tranquil open water.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n·         24 hour concierge<br />\r\n\r\n·         15 minutes from the City<br />\r\n\r\n·         Green open spaces<br />\r\n\r\n·         Private gym and spa facilities\r\n</p>\r\n \r\n<p>In the midst of one of the capital\'s most eclectic areas, Woodberry Down is a place that offers the tranquility of nature alongside a rich sense of community. The opening of the Woodberry sees years of hard work by the dedicated team behind the nature reserve come to fruition. This is the first time in 200 years that the former reservoir has been open to the public, and will remain open 365 days a year! With the offer of an unparalleled living experience beside one of the most unique natural sites in London, nowhere else in London offers such a varied place to live.</p>', 'Woodberry Down', 'Finsbury Park N4 2SB', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'woodberry-down', '', '', '2016-08-04 19:59:37', '2016-08-04 19:59:37', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=558', 0, 'property', '', 0),
