(569, 1, '2016-08-03 12:08:55', '2016-08-03 12:08:55', '<p>London Dock by St George, situated just moments from Tower Bridge, the Tower of London, St Katharine Docks and the City. This exciting new destination in the heart of London, a thriving new cultural quarter, featuring a magnificent choreographed central water feature and the finest selection of high quality new homes.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     Discover 7.5 acres of new public space<br />\r\n•     Indulge in hotel-style residents facilities<br />\r\n•     Move in from Q3 2016<br />\r\n•     Explore new places to eat, drink and enjoy\r\n</p>\r\n<p>London Dock is the perfect place to unwind over lunch or dinner in the vibrant surroundings of Gauging Square, a stunning new space with spectacular interactive water features and a thriving mix of shops, bars and restaurants.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a number of London underground and Docklands Light Railway stations within walking distance, London Dock offers quick and easy access to London&#39;s main financial centres of the City and Canary Wharf, as well as the exciting cultural and creative neighborhoods of Shoreditch, Whitechapel and Bermondsey.</p>\r\n', 'London Dock', 'Dock St, London E1', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'london-dock', '', '', '2016-08-04 20:00:46', '2016-08-04 20:00:46', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=569', 0, 'property', '', 0),
