(628, 1, '2016-08-03 14:17:13', '2016-08-03 14:17:13', '<p>Smithfield Square is a collection of luxury suites, 1 and 2 bedroom apartments benefiting from a concierge service, gym, underground parking and private gardens. Located on Hornsey High Street between Crouch End, Muswell Hill and Alexandra Palace, with central London just 15 minutes away, this unique development offers the perfect blend of London living.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     Award-winning developer<br />\r\n•     Excellent specification<br />\r\n•     London village lifestyle<br />\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Less then 300m from Hornsey rail station, Smithfield Square offers easy access to frequent rail services into Kings Cross within 17 minutes. Finsbury Park is only one stop away and provides connection to Victoria Line. Turnpike Lane Station is just a 10 minute walk away offering links on the Piccadilly line to the West End, Knightsbridge and direct access to Heathrow Airport. For travel by car, the road network links of A1, North Circular Road (A406) and M25 are all within easy reach.</p>\r\n', 'Smithfield Square', 'Hornsey N8 7QB', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'smithfield-square', '', '', '2016-08-05 13:24:06', '2016-08-05 13:24:06', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=628', 0, 'property', '', 0),
