(758, 1, '2016-08-04 13:10:55', '2016-08-04 13:10:55', '<p>At 68 storeys, South Quay Plaza is one of the tallest residential towers in Europe and has much to offer. With a unique combination of spectacular views over Canary Wharf and the City of London, eye-catching architecture and first class amenities; all built and designed with the exceptional quality that naturally comes with a Berkeley home. South Quay Plaza isn’t just about living up high, it\'s about living tall.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     One of the tallest residential towers in Europe designed by Foster &amp; Partners<br />  \r\n•     Residents spa, gymnasium and 20m swimming pool<br />\r\n•     1.6 acres of landscaped gardens<br />\r\n•     Residents club lounge &amp; terrace on the 56th floor<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Designed by Foster + Partners, South Quay Plaza is set to be one of the tallest residential buildings in Europe. Combining the highest quality of architecture, interior design and amenities, it also promotes sustainable high-rise living, which means creating not just a new landmark for London, but a vibrant, long-term community. Superbly located at a pivotal intersection of the capital\'s historic docks in canary Wharf, South Quay Plaza will create a vibrant, safe, mixed-use and sustainable waterside development of the highest design quality.  It will set the benchmark for future similar developments across the UK. South Quay Plaza’s slender 68-storey glass and steel tower will bring a new focal point to the London skyline and provide a new reason to live in Canary Wharf, the city’s prestigious, modern financial district.</p>', 'South Quay Plaza', 'London E14', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'south-quay-plaza', '', '', '2016-08-04 19:59:04', '2016-08-04 19:59:04', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=758', 0, 'property', '', 0),
