(781, 1, '2016-08-04 14:06:41', '2016-08-04 14:06:41', '<p>Chelsea is one of London’s iconic urban villages. Buzzing with history and culture, at its very heart is a hidden gem, Bolton Studios. Bolton Studios is located in the exclusive Bolton’s Conservation area in the Heart of Chelsea. Originally designed as a series of annexes for the large homes on Gliston Road, the Studios were created in the late 19th century in the adjoining back gardens, to serve the numerous artist in the area. These clever apartments offer double height ceilings in the living rooms, an abundance of smart storage solutions, top of the range Miele appliances, concierge and the ability to apply for a Kensington and Chelsea Parking Permit.</p>\r\n  \r\n<p>Whether you want to work out at state of the art gym facilities, sip an espresso at an out door cafe, pick up fresh produce at a farmer\'s market or shop at one of the many designer shops – Everything you could want can be found here on your doorstep.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Discreetly nestled between the expansive crescents of Gliston and Redcliffe Roads, Bolton Studios affords both privacy and security whilst providing everything Chelsea has to offer.</p>', 'Bolton Studios', 'Bolton Studios, 17B Gilston Road London SW10', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bolton-studios', '', '', '2016-08-05 13:03:34', '2016-08-05 13:03:34', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=781', 0, 'property', '', 0),
