(811, 1, '2016-08-04 15:30:32', '2016-08-04 15:30:32', '<p>The Buckingham apartments enjoy a centrality of location that few others possess. They sit at the nexus of London, surrounded by the best of British history, power and culture. The open space surrounding The Buckingham also frames some of Europe’s most elegant and beloved architectural landmarks, broadest avenues and grandest Royal Parks is a unique project that represents a once in a life time opportunity for interested parties to purchase a historical asset. The property comprises of 3 listed building which have been knocked through and converted in to 8 uber exclusive apartments. Out of these 6 apartments are for sale. The property over looks the Buckingham palace and is only 10 minutes away from Piccadilly and Mayfair by walk through St. James’s Park.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The development offers 1 bedroom to 3 bedroom options will all modern living amenities as well as private access apartments. The property is almost ready and will be handed over shortly. You will have the ability to go see the apartments and get a feel of how they will be to live in. Here are some features of the property:</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     Secure development with 24/7 security and concierge service<br />\r\n•     Top quality finish and fixtures<br />\r\n•     Ceiling Heights unto 3.7 Meters<br />\r\n•     Share of Freehold<br />\r\n</p>\r\n  \r\n  ', 'The Buckingham', '6-9 Buckingham Gate, London, SW1E', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-buckingham', '', '', '2016-08-05 12:48:36', '2016-08-05 12:48:36', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=811', 0, 'property', '', 0),
