(824, 1, '2016-08-04 15:59:39', '2016-08-04 15:59:39', '<p>An exclusive community of 34 premium residences, Hempel Gardens offers exquisite design, surroundings, and service. This is a new development in Bayswater, W2, moments from Hyde Park, set behind a period façade and uniquely arranged around a stunning private garden square.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Housed in a former boutique hotel with original Victorian frontage, these impeccable homesunite heritage and high-tech; history and future. Here, you’ll discover a combination of quintessentially British design, immaculate service, and direct views over a beautiful private square.</p>\r\n  \r\n<p>Hempel Gardens residents will experience a world-class concierge and full lifestyle management service. The developers have selected Rhodium to provide this unique service to Hempel Gardens. A true specialist in the super-prime sector, Rhodium is a pioneer of bespoke property and lifestyle management at the very highest levels.</p>\r\n  \r\n<p>The concierges will oversee the immaculate day-to-day running of the development, while dedicated teams discreetly address the needs of every resident. Drawing on an extensive, established network, residents and their guests get exclusive access to the very best of London. Uniquely, residents will also be offered their own management service. A specialist team of professionals will be available to residents. Working seamlessly with on-site teams, they will provide expert, consistent service and support on everything from plumbing to audio-visual technology.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More than a home, Hempel is the epitome of British luxury, with an authentic, timeless elegance shared by the whole Collection.</p>', 'Hempel Gardens', 'London W2', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hempel-gardens', '', '', '2016-08-05 12:47:19', '2016-08-05 12:47:19', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=824', 0, 'property', '', 0),
