(832, 1, '2016-08-04 17:07:40', '2016-08-04 17:07:40', '<p>Located adjacent to Hyde Park and Park Lane, Mayfair Park Residences aims to set a new benchmark for super- prime residential development in Mayfair. With detailed architecture that incorporates a beautiful Grade-II listed facade and views across to Hyde Park from both the Curzon Street and Stanhope Gate side, the development will offer 18 prestigious apartments serviced directly by one of the world’s most exclusive hotel groups – Dorchester Collection --- there is a direct physical connection to the adjacent 45 Park Lane Hotel, enabling a fully integrated 5 star hotel service.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     A scheme designed around the principle of seamless service<br />\r\n•     Interior design by Jouin Manku<br />\r\n•     Hotel services for all guests- there is a direct physical connection to the adjacent 45 Park Lane Hotel, enabling a fully integrated 5* hotel service.<br />\r\n•     24/7 Concierge<br />\r\n•     Valet Parking<br />\r\n•     20m pool<br />\r\n•     8,500 sq. ft. gym and 2 treatment rooms<br />\r\n•     Chauffeur driven house car<br />\r\n•     Secure underground car parking<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Mayfair Park Residences offers a selection of exclusive serviced apartments called the Dorchester Collection. Each apartment will be serviced by the adjoining 45 Park Lane Hotel. Choice apartments come with views of Hyde Park and Park Lane.</p>', 'Mayfair Park Residences', 'Mayfair, London', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mayfair-park-residences', '', '', '2016-08-05 12:45:10', '2016-08-05 12:45:10', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=832', 0, 'property', '', 0),
