(862, 1, '2016-08-04 18:09:25', '2016-08-04 18:09:25', '<p>A highly specified Penthouse apartment selection of two and three bedroom apartments and Penthouse in Dickens Yard\'s final phase, the Elizabeth Apartments. Located in close proximity to Ealing Broadway Underground station, Dickens Yard is set to benefit from the upcoming Crossrail service, the Elizabeth Line. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>From 24 minutes to Heathrow,12 minutes from Paddington and 30 minutes from the West End, Ealing Broadway Underground and rail stations offer fast and reliable connections to central London. From 2019, Crossrail will reduce journey times further, cutting trips to the City, Canary Wharf and elsewhere by up to fifty per cent. The nearby M4 and M25 road networks offer easy links to the rest of the UK - and beyond. *Source Transport for London.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Designed by leading urban architects John Thompson and Partners, Dickens Yard creates a dynamic yet safe new environment in the centre of Ealing. The energy and vitality of Dickens Yard and its unique fusion of historic buildings, cutting- edge architecture and modern facilities define a new focus for Ealing Town Centre. </p>', 'Dickens Yard', 'Ealing W5 2XA London w5', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dickens-yard', '', '', '2016-08-05 12:38:36', '2016-08-05 12:38:36', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=862', 0, 'property', '', 0),
