(876, 1, '2016-08-04 18:30:15', '2016-08-04 18:30:15', '<p>The Landau is a prestigious development in Farm Lane, Fulham. Drawing on this rich heritage, The Landau is a serene and quintessentially British oasis in the heart of a thriving London neighbourhood, comprised of 90 individually designed apartments in Fulham that offer a perfect balance of space and serenity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The elegantly designed building is constructed in warm Portland stone and Hammersmith London Stock, with contemporary windows and deep reveals. The 26 duplexes and 64 lateral apartments offer one to three bedrooms and spectacular penthouses on the top floor. All apartments have a balcony or outdoor space in which to relax and unwind.</p>  \r\n \r\n<p>Apartments at The Landau, including our duplexes, are individually designed but share a commitment to space and privacy. Classic materials, with contemporary design, combine to create a calm and seamless home environment. Luxurious finishes include caesarstone quartz worktops, European Oak Fendi hardwood floors, elite designer bronzed lever furniture and subtle recessed lighting.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>The Landau is situated in Fulham which is fast becoming one of London’s most sought-after areas for stylish living. Surrounded by a wealth of local neighbourhood amenities, The Landau\'s location will appeal to families needing quality accommodation close to the capital’s most respected schools, international buyers looking for a perfect pied-a-terre with easy access to the centre of town, and successful professionals seeking a cosmopolitan lifestyle with fast links to the City. A five minute walk to Fulham Broadway Underground Station (District Line) and an eight minute walk to West Brompton Station (District Line and London Overground), The Landau is perfectly situated to get around London’s key destinations with ease.</p>', 'The Landau', 'Fulham, London SW6 1QA', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-landau', '', '', '2016-08-04 20:29:58', '2016-08-04 20:29:58', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=876', 0, 'property', '', 0),
