(886, 1, '2016-08-04 18:30:47', '2016-08-04 18:30:47', '<p>Royal Arsenal Riverside is one of South East London\'s most exciting riverside addresses, occupying a prime location along the River Thames with a forthcoming on-site Crossrail Station and buzzing retail hub.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n•     On-site Thames Clipper service<br />\r\n•     Close proximity to London City Airport<br />\r\n•     Fantastic range of on-site amenities<br />  \r\n•     Over 1km of river walk<br />\r\n•     Breathtaking apartments<br />\r\n•     Forthcoming luxury spa and gym<br />\r\n•     300m away from National Rail and DLR stations<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Royal Arsenal Riverside is a superb riverside destination. With 5,000 new homes plus restaurants, bars, retails outlets and leisure facilities, all complemented by parks, beautiful riverside walks, and a rich history, it is truly is a sustainable new community.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Home to a forthcoming Crossrail station, residents will benefit from dramatically reduced journey times, including Canary Wharf in just 8 minutes (currently 28 minutes).</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Situated near the banks of the River Thames, in the Royal Borough of Greenwich, the homes will offer sensational Thames-side living. Open spaces are abundant, from the lawn and formal gardens of Wellington Park through to green corners, wide avenues and broad squares, the forthcoming 4 acre Waterfront Park and over 1km of river. </p>', 'Waterfront - Royal Arsenal Riverside', 'Woolwich SE18 6FR', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'waterfront-royal-arsenal-riverside', '', '', '2016-08-04 20:28:37', '2016-08-04 20:28:37', '', 0, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/?post_type=property&#038;p=886', 0, 'property', '', 0),
