(910, 1, '2016-08-04 19:45:35', '2016-08-04 19:45:35', '<p>One Nine Elms Is a Landmark Development, Part of London’s Most Important Regeneration Project in Decades. Two Iconic Towers Will House Premium Apartments and a Luxury Five-star Hotel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bold and Ambitious in Design, River Tower and City Tower are Destined to Be Amongst the Tallest Residential Buildings in Central London. Standing Out as Showstopping New Landmarks for the Capital.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Soaring over 50 storeys into the sky, the iconic towers of One Nine Elms will scale new heights and offer dramatic views reaching right across London and Beyond.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Residents Will Experience Unrivalled Views From the Upper Floors. At Mezzanine Level, an Innovative Floating Walkway Will Allow Them to Enjoy the Facilities of the Five-star Wanda Vista Hotel Without Stepping Outside.</p>', 'One Nine Elms', '1 Nine Elms Ln, London SW8', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '902-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-04 19:45:35', '2016-08-04 19:45:35', '', 902, 'http://brandstallion.com/eylsianglobal/2016/08/04/902-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
